Oh, Daddy! (1935)
Radio Lover (1936)
Como guionista
It's a Boy (1933)
A Southern Maid (1933)
Three Maxims (1936)
The Mill on the Floss (1937)
South American George (1943)
Theatre Royal (1943)
Champagne Charlie (1944)
Don Chicago (1945)


